Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:11.73,Opening - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}守りたい思いが胸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.65,Opening - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}燃やすよ
