Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.87,Opening - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}輝く時を待ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.04,Opening - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}涙をふるって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:27.13,Opening - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}この空に誓うから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.46,Opening - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}さあ　羽ばたこう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:33.63,Opening - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}無敵の勇気を広げ
