Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.81,Opening - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大きく手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:46.85,Opening - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}まだ誰も知らないあの空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:50.23,Opening - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}強く願い続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:56.45,Opening - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}それが翼になるよ
